data.description: Chadwick Beach Ocean Block! Only a few short steps to the ocean but NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE! It features 3 bds, 2 bths plus bonus room on 3rd level, this contemporary beach home has preferred amenities throughout w an open floor plan for optimal family gathering & entertaining. Featuring a lrg center island, custom cabinetry, qrtz countertops, recessed lighting, hdwd floors, central air, central vac, outside shower & dining patio. The bedrooms are spacious & the bonus third level deck has ocean views. Close enough to hear the waves, in this desirable family community with a full schedule of Summer activities. Tastefully furnished throughout. Great rental history, as well.  Relax with family & friends, enjoy the local attractions and take advantage of everything the Jersey Shore has to offer.
